			<p>Art Design and Illustration by Keith Gregg <br /> Twitter: <a href="http://twitter.com/keithmiketom" target="_blank">@keithmiketom</a> Web: <a href="http://keithgregg.com">keithgregg.com</a></p>
	    </article>
