	    	<div class="textbox">    	
		    	<p>I also write about what I do, whether it is Code Related (my developer hat), about Design or some Artworks I am working on. In any case, you can come and comment on what I am doing, and more importantly how I am doing, leaving suggestions and requests.</p>
		    </div>
